    .panel.panel-primary
      .panel-heading.text-center
        %h2
          %i.fa.fa-star.fa-spin.fa-fw
          <strong>#INTERITUS</strong> XM ANOMALY EVENT IN MELBOURNE
      .panel-body
        %strong Melbourne has been confirmed as a primary anomaly site for an event on May 17th as part of the <a href="http://google.com/+ingress/about">#INTERITUS</a> XM anomaly series. Find out more via our <a href="/community">Google+ community</a> and/or join the <a href="http://tinyurl.com/mu4kzge">anomaly community</a> to be actively involved in planning and don't forget to start collecting supplies for what will no doubt be an epic battle!
